'''Lmkḥla''' tamɣribit (s [[darija]]: مكحلة) tga yan wanaw zɣ wanawn ibckiḍn n uqqṛyan tiqbuṛin, ar tssmras ɣ wansa n tsrdast gr tmiḍi tiss ṣḍis d mraw d tizwiri n tmiḍi tiss si mraw, ɣilad ar ttili ɣ igdudn n iyysan ittwassnn s "Ttbuṛida".

Mzaraynt tmitar d tmẓlay n "Lmkḥla" tamṛṛukit f matta tmnaḍṭ illan ɣ tgldit,d tɣarast n uhyya-nns ar ttiri kigan n uffulls.

== Amazrar n uhyya ==
Ar ittili ɣ umazrar n uhyya n Lmkḥla tamṛṛukit kigan n tazzulin:

* Ayt iɣnba: nitni imhyyatn n iɣnbutn nna ttggan gis tifila n uzzal nna d-yuckan zɣ uruba, maka ad hyyun tiɣʷnba gr mitru d 1,8 mitru (iwbckiḍ) d tayṭ n anaw n 80 Sunitimtr i taymẓẓiyn, ilin-as ittsn id lftl n uzzal afad qqsḥnt.
* Izndayn: nitni gan imhyyatn n izndatn; anaw n bucfṛ, nna yttwassnn kigan, d wanaw n buḥbba nna ymslaɣn ɣ yat tftilt itbaqqayn. ikkatn Izndayn ar ssnfaln ɣ izndatn nna ɣ ttggan urɣ d wanas d nnqqrt.
* Inmazaln n uzyyn: kigan gisn iga zɣ udayn imṛṛukiyn nna yssnn i wzyyn n ibckiḍn d ifassn-nns, s tɣarast n ugr n wurɣ d nnqqrt d idrimn, d kkan-tt-nn ar ssmrasn s isufar zund ikʷccaḍ d lɛaj.

